{"tid":1379943,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"急症入院後48小時做乜嘢","createTime":"2019-07-29T01:41:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:09.000Z","uid":279848,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ddfdf2edf7b3fa30d178a8b7a9542847f130633a","tid":1379943,"uid":279848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T01:41:57.000Z","msg":"發夢見到有人咁樣同醫生講<br />\n<br />\n我而家望一邊兩隻眼不停閃光同黑影，好矇有兩個影<br />\n頭先啲嘢唔記得曬<br />\n好似斷咗邊咁樣<br />\n個朋友好似話我响喺度抽筋<br />\n而家感覺想嘔<br />\n個頭好痛<br />\n前幾日行山，畀蚊咬過<br />\n<br />\n响醫院發下夢<br />\n不是斷片<br />\n問自己係邊個<br />\n去咗邊一度<br />\n<br />\n咁樣要<br />\nconsult 眼科<br />\nCT Brain<br />\n驗血<br />\n仲可能要抽脊椎液<br />\n可以做之前又反口<br />\n話唔記得簽過同意書<br />\n跟著refusal form<br />\n但迫你出院前又同意番<br />\n。。。。"},{"pid":"0d088f926121e496a9a0dc651baf5c0a9587e8ec","tid":1379943,"uid":263485,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"唔知你 up 乜鳩。"},{"pid":"9df95933c04431e23fc48e3c72ef593b6aae779b","tid":1379943,"uid":136393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-29T02:27:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}